data.description: This cozy, Move-In Ready, home is available to make your Estate! Add your personal touches and this home is a true win! Located in the heart of Hudson. It is a ranch-style home on a large 9,375(sqft) square foot lot with plenty of room for storage, play structures, gardens/horticulture, landscaping, and vehicles... Tons of options. There is a park located right behind the house. Hudson is just 18 minutes from Brighton and 30 minutes from Denver so you can enjoy quiet country living but easy access to everything you need! Plus, the town is working to bring in even more convenience to its residents. A new BNSF Railway Logistics center is currently in development and coming soon to Hudson. This will bring in additional business. Again, with your finishing touches, this home can become an amazing Estate! The sky is truly the limit with this one. Easy access to I-76. Schedule a showing & enjoy (All renovations will be completed prior to closing).
